{% extends 'web/base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About us{% endblock %}

{% block body %}

    <div class="container-fluid text-center pt-5 mt-4 pb-5 mb-5 w-75">
        <h1 class="display-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <hr class="w-75 mb-4">
        <div class="text-left w-75 w-max-1000px mx-auto mb-5">
            <h2 class="mb-3">How J&WReady jewellery is produced?</h2>
            <h5 class="text-muted pl-4 pr-4">We are not producing the products that we are selling! We are a simple
                drop-shipping service. All of our products are ordered from Alibaba.</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="text-left w-75 w-max-1000px mx-auto mb-5">
            <h2 class="mb-3">How I can purchase a product?</h2>
            <h5 class="text-muted pl-4 pr-4">Simple, just create an account. Deposit certain ammount of money into your
                balance. And order the product from our <a href="{{ path("catalogue") }}">Catalogue</a></h5>
        </div>
        <div class="text-left w-75 w-max-1000px mx-auto mb-5">
            <h2 class="mb-3">How the product is delivered to me?</h2>
            <h5 class="text-muted pl-4 pr-4">We are using Alibaba existing and confirmed delivery network for
                transformation of products. You can track the delivered product status in your user dashboard.</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="text-left w-75 w-max-1000px mx-auto">
            <h2 class="mb-3">Am I able to return the ordered product?</h2>
            <h5 class="text-muted pl-4 pr-4">Due to the us being a start-up drop-shipping business, we are not accepting any refunds.</h5>
        </div>
    </div>

{% endblock %}
